## Decisions and Action Items

* **Consecutive WGLCs**: The chairs decided to run future WGLCs consecutively rather than concurrently to avoid reviewer fatigue and increase non-author response rates.
* **Park "Dorms"**: The "Dorms" draft will be parked until an active, concrete use case demands further development.

